Package com.futurice.cascade.i.assertion

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAssertion
    A chainable runtime assertTrue assertion for debugOrigin builds
    IAssertionOne<A>
    A chainable runtime assertTrue assertion for debugOrigin builds
    IAssertionTwo<A,B>
    A function accepting two arguments and returning true if all is normal and good.
    IBaseAssertion
    A marker interface to indicate that this is function to be performed probably at some point in the future with possibly a variable number of parameters and possibly a return value.
